number.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      is_training: Boolean. Controller of mechanism for dropout.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      causality: Boolean. If &lt;span class=&#34;literal&#34;&gt;true&lt;/span&gt;, units that reference the future are masked. &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      num_heads: An int. Number of heads.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      scope: Optional scope for `variable_scope`.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      reuse: Boolean, whether to reuse the weights of a previous layer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        by the same name.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    Returns&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;      A 3d tensor with shape of &lt;span class=&#34;params&#34;&gt;(N, T_q, C)&lt;/span&gt;  &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    &amp;#x27;&amp;#x27;&amp;#x27;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;    with tf.variable_scope&lt;span class=&#34;params&#34;&gt;(scope, &lt;span class=&#34;attr&#34;&gt;reuse&lt;/span&gt;=reuse)&lt;/span&gt;:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# Set the fall back option for num_units&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;keyword&#34;&gt;if&lt;/span&gt; num_units is None:&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;            num_units = queries.get_shape&lt;span class=&#34;params&#34;&gt;()&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;string&#34;&gt;.as_list&lt;/span&gt;[-1]&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        &lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;span class=&#34;line&#34;&gt;        &lt;span class=&#34;comment&#34;&gt;# Linear projections&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt